# Python / tooling caches
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/

# Local virtualenvs (must never enter Docker build context)
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/

# VCS / editor
.git/
.idea/
.vscode/

# Large / irrelevant artifacts for runtime images
**/dist/
**/node_modules/
**/htmlcov/
**/.coverage*
